&lt;li&gt;Develop bid strategies, win themes, value propositions, and competitive positioning in collaboration with leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead bid kick-offs, proposal plans, responsibility matrices, timelines, and structured review processes.&lt;/li&gt;
